{"tid":2434558,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Reddit 任命首位財務長準備上市","createTime":"2021-03-05T15:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T03:57:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9877cd8c2fa92cfb187274e5153ed4bcbb6a3606","tid":2434558,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕號稱「美國PTT」的知名網路論壇Reddit今（5）宣布，該公司已任命另一知名社群媒體Snap的首任財務長Drew Vollero，為該公司的首任財務長，以為Reddit的IPO做準備。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報導，全球知名的網路論壇Reddit今宣布，該公司正準備上市，而該公司的首任財務長Vollero，將在Reddit內部建立財務、審計和會計職能，並帶領公司完成上市過程。此前Vollero曾為玩具商美泰兒（Mattel）、Snap等公司營運財務業務。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\nReddit還在去年12月，收購了TikTok的競爭對手、同為社群APP的「Dubsmash」，該公司並已在2月籌集了2.5億美元的新資金，為Reddit最大筆的一輪集資，促Reddit的估值達到60億美元。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3457785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457785&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=0f78c94b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3457785&h=74a08ccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3457785</a>"},{"pid":"64efffe37eb3ddd5795f9ccdc251346fd04d55db","tid":2434558,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"升爆"},{"pid":"455fa26ec1aded479163b2088d7eea1dc6b6883b","tid":2434558,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"連登高登幾時上埋nasdaq<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}